HEADWORD: Shipper
<hw>Ship"per</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[See <er>Ship</er>,
<pos>n.</pos>, and cf. <er>Skipper</er>.]</ety> <def>One who sends goods
